@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

actor "用户" as U
participant "前端\n(Vue 2)" as FE
participant "网关\n(Spring Cloud Gateway)" as GW
participant "认证服务\n(edu-auth)" as Auth
database "Redis" as Redis
database "MySQL" as DB

U -> FE : 输入用户名和密码
FE -> GW : POST /auth/login\n{username, password}
GW -> Auth : 转发登录请求
Auth -> DB : 查询用户信息\nSELECT * FROM sys_user\nWHERE user_name = ?
DB --> Auth : 返回用户记录
Auth -> Auth : 验证密码\n(BCrypt匹配)
Auth -> Auth : 生成UUID\n作为user_key
Auth -> Redis : 存储LoginUser\nlogin_tokens:{user_key}\nTTL=720分钟
Auth --> GW : 返回JWT令牌\n{user_key, user_id, username}
GW --> FE : 返回access_token
FE -> FE : 存储令牌到localStorage
U <-- FE : 登录成功，跳转首页

note right of Auth
  双令牌机制：
  JWT仅承载身份标识
  权限数据存于Redis
end note

@enduml
